# YourStrat Build Order

Follow YOURSTRAT_BUILD.md §11 week by week. Verify each screen/endpoint end-to-end before the next.

- Week 1: skeleton, auth, onboarding, Today empty state
- Week 2: food scan loop, Today with meals
- Week 3: workouts, profile, net calories, ship prep

Use shared UI from `mobile/components/ui/`. Errors → Toast, not Alert.
